<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-12-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-12-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="218" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d218">
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Smythe</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName></hi>.</head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States to Santo
                                        Domingo</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Port au
                                    Prince</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-12-15"><hi rend="italic">December 15,
                                    1893</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Commandant killed at Azua, Santo Domingo. Bold attempt to assassinate
                            Heureaux. Meade<note n="†" xml:id="d218fn1">Consul at Santo Domingo
                                City.</note> cables American schooner attacked; two sailors wounded
                            at Azua. Have cabled instructions.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Smythe</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>